{"tid":1497511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要入機場都係得個幾個方法姐","createTime":"2019-08-23T03:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T10:05:01.000Z","uid":164590,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5a3a0a149b31bdc35c14678c786ed687a011454f","tid":1497511,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:59:25.000Z","msg":"1。嗰條路<br />\n2。機鐵沿途四個站<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你唔俾我入機場入邊我咪唔入囉</span></span>"},{"pid":"48640d080be4b70c70c4a397f3f266bb3d10ef76","tid":1497511,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:01:31.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推"},{"pid":"e105d81b767bbbc3e881133c9dc00313e548389f","tid":1497511,"uid":281926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pgzvoHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpgzvoHP.png&h=79a62f84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bef4075ccf90654148fd64b7c29dd651eeafe283","tid":1497511,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:06:26.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"3c688f0bf36b368c71a1cc1ad2e027cb4df4ab56","tid":1497511,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:08:07.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">搞到全世界經濟</span><br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多<span style=\"color: red;\">受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界陪葬</span>既時候，你覺得啲<span style=\"color: red;\">大國會唔會出聲？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>重點係揸車/搭車遊覽東涌令交通擠塞，癱瘓機場交通，唔係行入機場入面</strong><br />\n空管主任返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇</span>"},{"pid":"d23f9f5ac896ded13ba485375a59eee11e9633e2","tid":1497511,"uid":83558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:08:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7c0c37616b1c594fad22f9617bc6ce23b0be26","tid":1497511,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">612 721 811<br />\n<br />\n823 人鏈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;823 23:59死線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494948\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494948</a><br />\n<br />\n824 朝早7點機場<br />\n<br />\n824 晏晝1點觀塘<br />\n<br />\n825 荃葵青<b